Class Container<T>

java.lang.Object
org.example.Container<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of elements in this container
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<T>
public class Container<T> extends Object implements Iterable<T>
A generic container class that can hold a variable number of objects with a head property.
